		</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">A licensed cosmetologist Rachelle Weisberger joins women’s holistic health talk for women radio host Irina Wardas on Wednesday, May 23rd at 9:30 am PT / 12:30 pm ET LIVE</span></p>
