<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Rachelle’s career in the beauty industry has spanned more than two decades and has included creating my own line of holistic cosmetics.  <a href="http://www.rachelleweisberger.com/" rel="nofollow"> Rachelle Weisberger expanded her expertise </a>to the medical field serving as staff cosmetologist for a major plastic surgery and dermatology center in northern New Jersey, specializing in camouflage makeup for problem skin, post-cosmetic surgery and cancer patients.  As the beauty director of a chain of women’s fitness centers, Rachelle introduced an integrated beauty, health and fitness program.  She has traveled extensively throughout the United States giving seminars, consulting and sharing her expertise.<img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-3264" title="Rachelle Weisberger, skin care specialist" src="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/rachelleweisberger-110x150.jpg" alt="Beauty and Anti-Aging Remedies" width="110" height="150" /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">A licensed cosmetologist, makeup artist and skin care specialist, Rachelle Weisberger is proof that you can reach an advanced age and still stay vibrant, healthy, fit and beautiful without botox or cosmetic surgery.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff9900;"><strong>Callers are welcome to join the conversation: <em> (347)-857-4862</em></strong></span></p>
<h4><strong>Suggested Women’s Radio and Podcast Interview Questions</strong>:</h4>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">What aroused your interest in beauty and holistic beauty?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> Why are most women still feeling insecure about their looks?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> What are your recommendations for a skin care routine that will ensure beautiful skin for many years to come?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> What are some guidelines for applying makeup as we age.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> What are some healthy habits women can adopt that will enhance their beauty?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">How do the emotions impact a woman’s appearance?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> What are some of the ways to cope with stress?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> What words of encouragement would you give to women who are facing aging?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff9900;"><em><strong>Looking forward to your questions (347)-857-4862</strong></em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><em>Let us breathe, smile and dance at the end of the show together</em>.</span></p>
