<p><span style="font-size: medium;">From a young age he has experienced the ‘calling’ of ‘others’ who wish to pass on teachings and wisdoms in order we may make lighter work of our time here on Earth. Although, due to being brought up in a strict Catholic community, he was forced to ignore this information, he never forgot what he had received. For decades, Gaetano has been treating clients from all walks of life, regardless of faith or creed, believing that the healing power.<img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-2424" title="Gaetano Vivo" src="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/gaetano1-124x150.jpg" alt="Messages from the Angels of Transparency" width="124" height="150" /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Could wise and wonderful beings contact us from beyond this world and unveil our true potential? Would knowing that we really mattered enable us to uncover the truth behind our reason for living? The fascinating book <em>Messages from the Angels of Transparency: Powerful Words from Gentle Souls</em> offers answers, spiritual practices and comprehensive meditations by teacher, healer and author, Gaetano Vivo, which have the potential to strengthen, heal and transform lives and bring hope and inspiration. </span></p>
