<p><span style="font-size: medium;">What are the seven energy wheels?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">How does the ‘state’ of each energy wheel affect our well-being?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">How can we repair a stationary/blocked energy wheel?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">You have also dealt with many people in the medical and scientific professions, can you share some of their experiences with your work and how it complements what they do?</span></p>
