		</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Autho</span>r<span style="font-size: medium;"> Russell Irving joins women’s holistic health talk radio host Irina Wardas on Wednesday, February 8th at 9:30 am PT / 12:30 pm <strong></strong>ET LIVE</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/MP3/BR31.mp3">Listen:</a> Holistic Health Talk Podcasts and Women Radio Show Topic</strong>: Don&#8217;t Overlook the Obvious: How to Improve and Relationship or Marriage</span></h2>
