		</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Author and Spiritual Healer Patty Shaw joins women’s holistic health talk for radio host Irina Wardas on Wednesday, December 28th at 9:30 am PT / 12:30 pm <strong></strong>ET LIVE</span></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/MP3/BR22.mp3" rel="nofollow">Listen</a>: Holistic Health Talk for Women Radio Show Topic:</strong></span><span style="font-size: medium;"> Alternative healing modalities as presented in Patty’s book; The Healer’s Almanac<br />
