<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Free Gift</strong>:<a href="http://www.healingwithpattyshaw.com/launch-bonuses" rel="nofollow"> click to get</a></span> <span style="font-size: medium;">Five Get Healthy Stay Healthy Seminar audio’s</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><strong><em><span style="color: #ff6600;">Live, holistic health talk for women radio and podcast streams from</span> <a href="http://www.blogtalkradio.com/NaturalCounselor" rel="external nofollow">the host page</a></em></strong></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Patty Shaw is a Spiritual Healer, Co-owner of Coventry Creations and author of Healers Almanac, Journey into Health with Wisdom from the 21<sup>st</sup> Century Goddesses.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Patty Shaw has been interested in the way we heal for most of her life. As the second oldest of nine, Patty started helping her mom tend to sick kids at an early age and paid close attention to how her mom handled it all. When she became a mom herself she took her mom&#8217;s strategy and added to it and started consulting many different kinds of health practitioners to help her keep her kids feeling healthy and energetic.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">With all the great information she collected, a book was born: Healer’s Almanac, Journey into Health with Wisdom from the 21st Century Goddesses. This is a book about alternative healing and about Patty&#8217;s personal healing journey. This book is filled with information, <img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-1595" title="Author Patty Shaw" src="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Patty-100x150.jpg" alt="Alternatie Healing" width="100" height="150" />inspiration and gorgeous goddesses that will guide your way into a happy and healthy life with meditations and words of encouragement. Her Book launch date is January 5th 2012 with amazon.com.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> Patty also developed her own healing talents and became a <a href="http://www.Healingwithpattyshaw.com " rel="nofollow">healer practitioner </a>certified through the Universal Church of the Masters, a transformational yoga instructor and a reiki master. Patty is passionate about helping people whether it&#8217;s in her private practice or at her Reiki Clinic. Patty is also co-owns and is Vice President of Coventry Creations – makers of magical candles.</span></p>
