<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Loa teaches her one-of-a-kind mind and body-sculpting class fusing elements of yoga, guided meditation, energy and strength training in premiere gyms in the Los Angeles area. Loa designed and leads the All Health&#8217;s Breaking Loose Wellness Boot Camp, the curriculum which inspired and gave birth to this book. You can follow her bi-weekly column in the La Canada Valley Sun (a division of the LA Times) also entitled “All Health’s Breaking Loose.”</span></p>
