<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/MP3/BR20.mp3" rel="nofollow">Listen:</a> Health Talk for Women’s Podcasts and Radio Show Topic:</strong></span> <span style="font-size: medium;">Paleo Diet and Beyond for a Longer a Happier Life</span>;<span style="font-size: medium;"> Primal Body and Mind for Total Health.</span></h2>
