<h2><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><strong><!-- google_ad_section_start --><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/MP3/BR14.mp3" rel="nofollow">Listen:</a> Health Talk for Women Radio and Podcast Topic: Conscious Breathing and Restorative Yoga for Healing<span id="more-1318"></span><!-- google_ad_section_end --></strong></strong></span></h2>
