<p><span style="font-size: medium;">What advice would you give other women struggling to heal from their breast cancer experience?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff9900;"><em><strong>Looking forward to your questions (347)-857-4862</strong></em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><em>Let us breathe, smile and dance at the end of the <a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com">show</a> together</em>.</span></p>
