			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com">Holistic Health Women&#039;s Podcasts and Radio</a></p><p style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 15px; width:240px;">
		<img src="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Mindy-e1298861200334-150x150.jpg" width="240" />
		</p><p><span id="more-58"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Founder of Green Scentsations and author Mindy Green joined Holistic Health Talk for Women radio show host Irina Wardas</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>Holistic Women&#8217;s Radio Show Topic for Discussion:</strong> <!-- google_ad_section_start -->Homemade Skin Care Treatments, Beauty Secrets and Spa Remedies for Home Pampering<!-- google_ad_section_end --></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Mindy Green is a genuine, national authority on botanicals with 35 years experience in the natural products and health care industries. She is a nationally certified Registered Aromatherapist and has served on the education committees of the National Association of Holistic Aromatherapists and the Aromatherapy Registration Council. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> Mindy has authored three books, including <em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Aromatherapy-Complete-Guide-Healing-Art/dp/1580911897?&amp;camp=212361&amp;linkCode=wey&amp;tag=naturalcouc01-20&amp;creative=380733">Aromatherapy: A Complete Guide to the Healing Art, Natural Perfumes: Simple Aromatherapy</a> Recipes, and Calendula</em>, as well as over 50 articles. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">An active educator and lecturer, Mindy has lectured at Andrew Weil’s reputable integrative medicine program at the University of Arizona and Bastyr University, among others. As a consultant and speaker, she specializes in product development, botanical therapies and value-added aromatherapy.<img class="alignright size-full wp-image-59" title="Pamper Yourself with Anti-Aging Beauty Remedies on Women Radio" src="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Mindy-e1298861200334-150x150.jpg" alt="Pamper Yourself with Anti-Aging Beauty Remedies on Women Radio" width="150" height="150" /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"> Mindy’s vast credentials and positions in botany, aromatherapy and cosmetics also include her current role as Cosmeceuticals Scientific Advisory Board Member for the Supply Side West trade show and conference, in addition to being a professional member of the American Herbalists Guild and serves as committee chair for botanicals in cosmetics for the American Herbal Products Association. From 1995 to 2003, Mindy was on the faculty of the Rocky Mountain Center for Botanical Studies, co-owned the California School of Herbal Studies from 1985 to 1995; and from 2003 to 2009, Mindy worked in the botanical research division of Aveda’s Research &amp; Development department as their clinical aromatherapist.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Currently, Mindy is owner of <a href="http://www.greenscentsations.com">Green Scentsations, LLC </a>and enjoys writing, teaching and speaking, which takes her all over the world. She holds a M.S. degree in Health &amp; Human Sciences and B.S, degree in Holistic Health Sciences, both from Columbia Pacific University.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">How can one turn their bathroom into a day spa?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">What is your favorite way to pamper yourself in a home spa setting?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Give an example of how to incorporate herbs or essential oils into a home spa treatment</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Bath salts are a pricey item in high end spas. How would one make that at home?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">What is the one skin care treatment that can be done at home that is comparable to what you would get at a spa?</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;">What is the best self applied beauty treatment that is beneficial for everyone?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Anti-aging facials&#8230;homemade body scrub recipe&#8230;.beauty foods&#8230;<em>Breathe, smile and be happy.</em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">© Irina Wardas, HHC</span></p>
<p><a href="http://www.holistichealthtalkradioforwomen.com/18/pamper-yourself-with-anti-aging-beauty-remedies/">Skin Care Treatments and Home Spa Secrets for Pampering with Author Mindy Green</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
